{"TopicId":210961,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"The 100,000 metre and back death-defying speed challenge","CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-06T20:10:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-06T20:10:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery simple. Fly to 100,000 metres and then return to Kerbin as fast as possible.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ERules: \u003C/strong\u003EStock and DLC only. No physics altering mods or cheats. The craft must be Kerbaled and your Kerbal(s) must survive. Touchdown is defined as a complete stop.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOtherwise, anything goes. You can build any type of vehicle.\u00A0 You can destroy any number of parts, including the entire vessel.\u00A0 If your Kerbal arrives physically intact (we cannot account for emotional trauma) you pass.\u00A0\u00A0 Take video and/or screenshots at takeoff, apogee and landing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThree categories:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Take off from \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E and land at \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E (anywhere within\u00A0 the flat area just around the complex).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Take off from and land anywhere (including tops of mountains). In other words, game the terrain.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Take off and land horizontally.\u00A0 In this case, the craft needs to land intact (defined as whatever parts it still had just before contacting the ground need to remain in good condition).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe idea came from watching \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/112420-shadowzone/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022112420\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/112420-shadowzone/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ShadowZone\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s recent attempt on the Minmus speed run challenge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLEADERBOARD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207172-camacju/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022207172\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207172-camacju/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@camacju\u003C/a\u003E 2:04!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/190194-farmerben/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022190194\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/190194-farmerben/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@farmerben\u003C/a\u003E3:36\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022181256\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181256-klapaucius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Klapaucius\u003C/a\u003E\u00A03:44\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-12-10T08:12:39Z\u0022 title=\u002212/10/2022 08:12  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 10, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-09T10:01:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is my attempt. I just squeaked in under 4 mintues at 3:58.\u00A0 I have no idea if you can do it faster this way or on a more gradual trajectory.\u00A0 I could do better. I still don\u0027t have the return optimized.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/uRyXRvAXW8I\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/uRyXRvAXW8I \u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-09T10:13:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3:44\u00A0 That was a very hard landing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/1BOLs6qlfmg?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022100000 Speed Challenge attempt 2\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-12-09T10:14:50Z\u0022 title=\u002212/09/2022 10:14  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 9, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"farmerben","CreatedById":190194,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-09T12:43:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3:36\u00A0 I started with 4 mammoth engines onioned on to this stage.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022screenshot29.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002260.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/kKx0ync/screenshot29.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T07:51:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI took the More Boosters approach all the way, with a time of 2:04.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022nPsOngB.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nPsOngB.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLaunch. Lots of Mammoth engines!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022lb16I2X.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/lb16I2X.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst stage is empty after 5 seconds\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022ItLxDYJ.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ItLxDYJ.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSecond stage is empty after 13 seconds\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022JHBZiDi.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/JHBZiDi.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThird stage is empty after 30 seconds. The rest of my engines are facing downward so I don\u0027t have to turn around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022KlJDRVm.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KlJDRVm.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApoapsis - I started the Mammoth engine burn too late. Oh well\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022NyOiVZu.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/NyOiVZu.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA cluster of Sepratron motors gives some impulse back towards Kerbin\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022oHWpTws.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/oHWpTws.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe cargo bay is aerodynamically optimized so it doesn\u0027t have much drag\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022hDnJZLV.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/hDnJZLV.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI open the service bay doors, turning the sepratron array into a giant air brake. This slows me down very quickly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022Ov024K7.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Ov024K7.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nParachutes deployed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022MGkWoLT.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/MGkWoLT.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStationary at 2:03!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s the full video:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/d75Wvmn5nJA?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022100km altitude return challenge - 2:03\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T08:01:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224207273\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210961\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221670658716\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207172\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022camacju\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, camacju said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI took the More Boosters approach all the way, with a time of 2:04.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was awesome!\u00A0 The sepratron cluster was brilliant.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI reckon you can make sub 2 minutes just by changing out your chutes.\u00A0 I found the big heat shield was a really good chute in that it acts very fast.\u00A0 While I did have regular chutes, I deployed them just as the shield hit and bouced/exploded, leaving me with an intact landing can.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-12-10T08:04:07Z\u0022 title=\u002212/10/2022 08:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 10, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T08:05:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI suspect sub-2 is possible just from flying this existing craft better. I do have ideas to go significantly faster however.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-10T08:09:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many G\u0027s do you reckon Jeb just endured?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, just added a third category--horizontal takeoff and landing.\u00A0 \u00A0Started thinking about it while getting myself a snack.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-12-10T08:13:36Z\u0022 title=\u002212/10/2022 08:13  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 10, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}